lyTime":"2021-04-29T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"我決定咗箍Invisalign，剝埋智慧齒就上箍，感覺揀啱咗診所，好睇醫生姑娘都好nice好好，冇咁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231bf476613624e047825e915160c3d7c3127b6e","tid":2421524,"uid":221317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"戴固定器後，覆診要再收費？"},{"pid":"df3a2012c19e9cb7a87cb5ba7ceefb81e163519b","tid":2421524,"uid":377175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231bf476613624e047825e915160c3d7c3127b6e","tid":2421524,"uid":221317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"戴固定器後，覆診要再收費？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:46:28.000Z","msg":"間間唔同㗎喎應該"},{"pid":"c4b5f73bfb3d46bac883d70c5176d02cb8f08350","tid":2421524,"uid":221317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df3a2012c19e9cb7a87cb5ba7ceefb81e163519b","tid":2421524,"uid":377175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"231bf476613624e047825e915160c3d7c3127b6e","tid":2421524,"uid":221317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"戴固定器後，覆診要再收費？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:46:28.000Z","msg":"間間唔同㗎喎應該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:49:25.000Z","msg":"我嗰間只包首6個月<br />\n當每3個月見一見醫生<br />\n即只包 2次🥲<br />\n <br />\n所以想問下大家啲收費如何<br />\n<br />\n似乎往後固定器覆診都幾大支出"}]}